                        <description><![CDATA[<p>The <code>paige/icon</code> shortcode displays a web font icon.</p>
<h2 id="class-parameter">Class parameter</h2>
<p>Code:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-go-html-template" data-lang="go-html-template"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">p</span> <span class="na">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&#34;display-1&#34;</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Icon: <span class="cp">{{</span><span class="err">&lt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">paige</span><span class="err">/</span><span class="nx">icon</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&#34;bi bi-github&#34;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">&gt;</span><span class="cp">}}</span><span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">p</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>Result:</p>
<p class="display-1">Icon: 









<span class="paige-shortcode-icon"><i class="bi bi-github" ></i></span>
</p>
<h2 id="title-parameter">Title parameter</h2>
<p>Code:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-go-html-template" data-lang="go-html-template"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">p</span> <span class="na">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&#34;display-1&#34;</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Icon: <span class="cp">{{</span><span class="err">&lt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">paige</span><span class="err">/</span><span class="nx">icon</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&#34;bi bi-github&#34;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">title</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&#34;GitHub&#34;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">&gt;</span><span class="cp">}}</span><span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">p</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>Result:</p>
<p class="display-1">Icon: 









<span class="paige-shortcode-icon"><i class="bi bi-github"  title="GitHub" ><span class="visually-hidden">GitHub</span></i></span>
</p>
<h2 id="url-parameter">Url parameter</h2>
<p>Code:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-go-html-template" data-lang="go-html-template"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">p</span> <span class="na">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&#34;display-1&#34;</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Icon: <span class="cp">{{</span><span class="err">&lt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">paige</span><span class="err">/</span><span class="nx">icon</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&#34;bi bi-github&#34;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">url</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&#34;https://github.com/willfaught/paige&#34;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">&gt;</span><span class="cp">}}</span><span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">p</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>Result:</p>
<p class="display-1">Icon: 









<span class="paige-shortcode-icon"><a href="https://github.com/willfaught/paige" ><i class="bi bi-github" ></i></a></span>
</p>]]></description>
                    

